repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;'\" style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:;\">Students are expected to do 60-90 minutes of outside study outside per class session.</span>"}, "評価": {"教科書/Required texts0": ["No textbook. Learning materials will be provided by the instructor. \nStudents will be expected to access online sources for information about foreign cultures, therefore a notebook PC is recommended.&nbsp;"], "学位授与の方針との関連Relationship to Diploma Policy0": ["Each subject is placed on the curriculum based on the Diploma Policy (DP) and Curriculum Policy (CP) established by each faculty and graduate school. \nBy studying this subject with the DP and CP in mind, you will develop the abilities expected by each faculty and graduate school. \nThe DP, CP and curriculum table (list of subjects, etc.) of each faculty and graduate school are posted in the link below, so please use it as a reference for your study plan. \nhttps://kwic.kwansei.ac.jp/cabinet/reference?typeCd=0&amp;cabinetId=557&amp;directLink=1 \n*This is a link to kwic (only current students can view it)"], "成績評価Grading0": ["種別　Type備考　Note", "割合　Percentage", "評価基準等　Grading Criteria etc."], "成績評価Grading1": ["その他／Others (99)", "100 %", "Midterm Project 20%, Final Project 30%, Discussions 20%, Class Notebook 10%; Classwork and Participation 20%"], "成績評価Grading2": ["備考　Note 出席、遅刻の制度については以下URL先をご確認ください。/ Please refer to the following URL for details regarding the attendance and tardiness policy.https://kwic.kwansei.ac.jp/cabinet/area/detail?areaId=7144&amp;directLink=1"], "備考Note0": ["To take this class, you must apply for level certification in advance. For details, please check the \"Course Registration Procedures\" at the following URL (KWIC Cabinet)."], "備考Note1": ["英語インテンシブ・プログラム　履修について"], "備考Note2": ["2026年01月22日 11時15分36秒"], "項番No.0": [], "項番No.1": ["2026年度", "春学期／Spring", "木曜２時限／Thursday 2", "春学期／Spring", "４別－２０３"]}, "campas": 0, "name": "【300】Cult